      "Generated via AI-assisted analysis of Psalm 23. Draws on Brueggemann and Bellinger's 'Psalms' (NCBC), Keller's 'A Shepherd Looks at Psalm 23,' and Davis's 'Getting Involved with God.' Grammatical shift analysis informed by Alter's 'The Art of Biblical Poetry.' Shepherding practices informed by Borowski's 'Every Living Thing.'"
