      "Generated via AI-assisted analysis of Psalm 103. Draws on Mays's 'Psalms' (Interpretation), Allen's 'Psalms 101-150' (WBC), and Brueggemann's 'The Message of the Psalms.' Exodus 34:6-7 creed analysis informed by Spieckermann's 'God's Steadfastness' and Fretheim's 'God and World in the Old Testament.' Hesed concept informed by Sakenfeld's 'The Meaning of Hesed in the Hebrew Bible.'"
