    sourceTier: "ai_assisted",
    sourceNotes:
      "Generated via AI-assisted analysis of Psalm 139. Draws on Allen's 'Psalms 101-150' (WBC), Goldingay's commentary, and Brueggemann's 'The Message of the Psalms.' Omniscience and freedom discussion informed by Fretheim's 'The Suffering of God' and Brueggemann's 'Theology of the Old Testament.' Surveillance parallels draw on Zuboff's 'The Age of Surveillance Capitalism.'"
